org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HLAM

Interface RtAction

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RtActionImpl

    public interface RtAction
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Rt Action'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Atomic
    • Synch Kind
    • Msg Size
    • Base Behavioral Feature
    • Base Invocation Action
    See Also:
    HLAMPackage.getRtAction()
